<subSubSection pageId="490" pageNumber="491" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="490" pageNumber="491">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="490" pageNumber="491">This species is found from southeastern Pennsylvania to Iowa (Wickham 1888: 82; King 1914: 323; Jaques and Redlinger 1946: 297), south to southern Louisiana and central Florida including the Panhandle (Peck and Thomas 1998: 19) [see Allen 1972: Fig. 160]. Old specimens simply labeled from Massachusetts and Oklahoma are known (Allen 1972: 144).</paragraph>
